    "name": "Broken Pieces",
    "steam_appid": 1293730,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/6333eff72528b1257f8cd69b9e48d68b.avif?t=1768950896\" width=600 height=172 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Broken Pieces</strong>主创有<strong>5 人</strong>，是法国游戏开发工作室<strong>Elseware Experience</strong>推出的第一款游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>当伊利斯和未婚夫决定离开城市生活来到法国海岸附近定居时，她没有想到自己最终会孤身一人。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>现在，伊利斯深陷各种奇怪的现象和冷战后的黑暗氛围，她必须调查圣埃克希尔地区、此地的仪式崇拜，以及俯瞰海岸的灯塔，解开笼罩在这里的谜团。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Broken Pieces 是一款动感十足、以法国为背景的调查和冒险视频游戏。游戏让你扮演伊利斯，一位 30 多岁的女性。她发现自己身处圣埃克希尔村，一个让人想起布列塔尼的虚构地区。无法解释的超自然现象发生之后，伊利斯就被困住了，孤身一人，连时间都停滞了。你的调查从这里开始……</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playtime :9 到 12 小时。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持 和 DLSS。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/52b774d09f032f00df74ea97c01dabd9.avif?t=1768950896\" width=600 height=172 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索 1990 年代的圣埃克希尔及其周边地区。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在标准第三人称视角及与90年代传奇游戏系列配套的完全修改版镜头系统之间选择，后者旨在提供更大的灵活性和玩家掌控力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任何情况下都可以在 2 个镜头角度之间切换，或者进入第一人称视角近距离观察四周。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与环境互动，了解更多你在圣埃克希尔发生的事情。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/2df54a369c366e438d1833dafa799c8b.poster.avif?t=1768950896\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/2df54a369c366e438d1833dafa799c8b.webm?t=1768950896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/2df54a369c366e438d1833dafa799c8b.mp4?t=1768950896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/3d68b2d4390a852f9cd2d18a0fa02e0f.avif?t=1768950896\" width=600 height=172 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的调查将按电影节奏被打断，动作完全由手持相机捕捉。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的冒险中尽情享受惊悚片的气氛。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/20b15c3fada319e0bc4d70eb050dcd53.poster.avif?t=1768950896\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/20b15c3fada319e0bc4d70eb050dcd53.webm?t=1768950896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/20b15c3fada319e0bc4d70eb050dcd53.mp4?t=1768950896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/44ac7f2fafd7b11bf20bd7add0bf6aa5.avif?t=1768950896\" width=600 height=172 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意手表上的时间；你必须在夜幕降临之前回家。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理你的库存量并确保携带取得进展所需的物品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的主要和次要任务中提供了各种额外的互动元素，例如老式街机。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >改变圣埃克希尔的天气以开辟新的道路或解开挡路的谜题。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/f790a244881f6994b5357e422eec3c7c.poster.avif?t=1768950896\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/f790a244881f6994b5357e422eec3c7c.webm?t=1768950896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/f790a244881f6994b5357e422eec3c7c.mp4?t=1768950896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/a112259642a70929d178fea60ebbf728.avif?t=1768950896\" width=600 height=172 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会发现一些磁带，可以从中提取线索帮助进行调查。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用磁带录音机快进或倒带，找到你需要的信息。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索圣埃克希尔村的同时收听磁带，享受无缝的探索体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索皮埃尔为伊利斯创作的音乐，这些音乐将一路伴随你的冒险。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/2d9472ddc68f989d39bffba12043931e.poster.avif?t=1768950896\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/2d9472ddc68f989d39bffba12043931e.webm?t=1768950896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/2d9472ddc68f989d39bffba12043931e.mp4?t=1768950896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/dfcb6a4f60d791085cff3112c5aacc3f.avif?t=1768950896\" width=600 height=172 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过使用固定镜头角度的独特战斗系统面对具有挑战性的敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用你的能力躲避敌人或将他们保持在一定距离以更好地击败他们。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过喝冰箱里的饮料、在长凳上小睡或在床上安睡整晚恢复生命值。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作高品质弹药并升级你的枪支以提高战斗能力。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/db6965da1898755329917e6c2d4c9440.poster.avif?t=1768950896\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/db6965da1898755329917e6c2d4c9440.webm?t=1768950896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1293730/extras/db6965da1898755329917e6c2d4c9440.mp4?t=1768950896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
